30b3ea4c25253e2ce673fe6b75b31a8f6288999b.query:
SELECT row_to_json(t) as "stylesheet!: sqlx::types::Json<Stylesheet>"
            FROM (
                SELECT id, value FROM meta.styles WHERE id = $1
            ) t

4cc729ef5079b85f225afddab8591413cf872c31.query:
SELECT row_to_json(jobs) as "status_info!: sqlx::types::Json<StatusInfo>" 
            FROM meta.jobs WHERE job_id = $1

7d0fea1e38d74daebcc615d0bfe5066cb5e7e137.query:
SELECT collection as "collection!: sqlx::types::Json<Collection>" 
            FROM meta.collections WHERE id = $1

88e0608fdea26037ed1596644f479efb3bd21898.query:
SELECT results as "results!: sqlx::types::Json<Results>"
            FROM meta.jobs
            WHERE job_id = $1

93331560b0436539064c711f3169a5e3ea571ec5.query:
SELECT array_to_json(array_agg(row_to_json(t))) as "styles: sqlx::types::Json<Vec<Style>>"
            FROM (
                SELECT id, title, links FROM meta.styles
            ) t

cf816e1e756813550be18810489c6f52b9deb11e.query:
SELECT array_to_json(array_agg(collection)) as "collections: sqlx::types::Json<Vec<Collection>>" 
            FROM meta.collections
            WHERE collection ->> 'type' = 'Collection'
